## 🌿 Step 6 — Get MongoDB Connection String

1. Go to **[mongodb.com/cloud/atlas](https://mongodb.com/cloud/atlas)** → Login
2. You'll see your cluster → Click **"Connect"**
3. Click **"Drivers"**
4. Under **"Add your connection string"** — copy that string. Looks like:
```
mongodb+srv://mongodb+srv://shopabhi:shopabhi@cluster0.dqjjz8f.mongodb.net/?appName=Cluster0